edia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The controversial performance\", \"from\": 5733, \"to\": 5762}, {\"ngram\": \"criticism\", \"from\": 5768, \"to\": 5777}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 5783, \"to\": 5790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the ceremony's artistic director denied that, saying the performance was instead inspired by Greek mythology and meant to celebrate the gods of Olympus, notThe Last Supper.\", \"from\": 5838, \"to\": 6014, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5935, \"end\": 5950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"score\": 0.9999999989940989, \"rank\": 1.0063006590439028e-09, \"text\": \"Greek mythology\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}, {\"begin\": 5986, \"end\": 5993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"score\": 0.999964273673603, \"rank\": 3.572760309133353e-05, \"text\": \"Olympus\", \"types\": [\"Q8502\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mount_Olympus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony's artistic director\", \"from\": 5842, \"to\": 5874}, {\"ngram\": \"the performance\", \"from\": 5895, \"to\": 5910}, {\"ngram\": \"the gods\", \"from\": 5974, \"to\": 5982}, {\"ngram\": \"notThe Last Supper\", \"from\": 5995, \"to\": 6013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Others have speculated that it is actually more reminiscent of Jan van Bijlert's paintingThe Feast of the Gods.\", \"from\": 6015, \"to\": 6126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6078, \"end\": 6093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_van_Bijlert\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jan van Bijlert\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_van_Bijlert\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jan_van_Bijlert\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Others\", \"f